metadata.title: Synonymous 3 Pack Reusable Mop Pad Compatible with Swiffer Sweeper Wet Pads, Compatible with Swiffer Sweeper 2 in 1 mop
features: The Synonymous replacement microfiber mop pads are compatible with the Sweeper microfiber spray and vac mop. The washable pads are 10.5 x 4.5 inch to fit the small mop.
The durable microfiber cloth mop refill are machine washable and can be used over 100 times. To ensure they come clean, it is best to soak immediately after use.
